ubuntu系统下命令行安装万以后，我们需要修改
    sudo vim /etc/mysql/mysql.conf.d/mysqld.cnf
在其中修改如下：
    [mysqld]
    #
    # * Basic Settings
    #
    user            = mysql
    pid-file        = /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.pid
    socket  = /var/run/mysqld/mysqld.sock
    port            = 3306
    datadir = /var/lib/mysql
    # bind-address		= 127.0.0.1
    # mysqlx-bind-address	= 127.0.0.1
修改结束后：
    service mysql restart;





关于密码：
    1.查看 mysql 初始的密码策略
        SHOW VARIABLES LIKE 'validate_password%';
    2.设置密码验证强度等级
        set global validate_password.policy=MEDIUM;
    3.设置密码长度
        set global validate_password.length=4;
    4.修改密码
        ALTER USER 'root'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';



VS code连接数据库之前，先在Extensions里面搜索mysql，完了install:
    MySQL
    MySQL Syntax

在非root权限下也可以访问数据库：
    mysql> USE mysql;
    mysql> CREATE USER 'kwj-at-lzu'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'YOUR_PASSWD';
    mysql> GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO 'kwj-at-lzu'@'localhost';
    mysql> UPDATE user SET plugin='auth_socket' WHERE User='kwj-at-lzu';
    mysql> FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
    mysql> exit;

    sudo service mysql restart
    然后在root权限下执行命令：
        grant system_user on *.* to 'root';
    最后执行：
        alter user 'kwj-at-lzu'@'localhost' identified with mysql_native_password by 'code';